  "build": {
    "buildCommand": "rtk tsc --noEmit 2>&1 | tail -3",
    "testCommand": "rtk gh pr create --title \"dev → main: Phase 8-12 功能合并\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\n\n合并 dev 分支的 Phase 8–12 所有功能到 main，准备首次部署。\n\n### 主要变更\n\n- **Phase 8 选秀核心** — 蛇形选秀完整流程（队长面板、围观页、超时自动 pick、事务并发安全）\n- **v2 赛制引擎** — 5 个 StageExecutor（round-robin / double-elim / single-elim / swiss / gsl-group）、advanceTiers 取代 advance、entrySeeds 种子轮空\n- **Phase 11.5 选手数据** — 排行榜（多排序+位置筛选）、MVP 投票、选手个人页跨赛季数据聚合、队伍数据卡片\n- **认证系统** — Email+Password 登录替代 Magic Link（#46）\n- **测试覆盖** — validator / state machine / lib / format executor / server action / component 共 80+ 测试\n- **部署准备** — vercel.json cron 配置、CRON_SECRET、GitHub Actions CI\n\n### 文件变更\n\n共 50 个提交，涉及约 120+ 文件。\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] 本地 `pnpm dev` 启动正常\n- [ ] `pnpm tsc --noEmit` 类型检查通过\n- [ ] `pnpm test` 全部通过\n- [ ] Vercel 预览部署正常\n- [ ] 生产环境可正常访问\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\"",
    "lintCommand": "pnpm lint",
    "devCommand": "pnpm dev",
    "scripts": {
      "dev": "NODE_OPTIONS='--dns-result-order=ipv4first' next dev",
      "build": "next build",
      "start": "next start",
      "lint": "next lint",
      "type-check": "next typegen && tsc --noEmit",
      "db:generate": "drizzle-kit generate",
      "db:push": "NODE_OPTIONS='--dns-result-order=ipv4first' drizzle-kit push",
      "db:studio": "NODE_OPTIONS='--dns-result-order=ipv4first' drizzle-kit studio",
      "test": "vitest run",
      "test:watch": "vitest",
      "test:coverage": "vitest run --coverage",
      "test:e2e": "playwright test",
      "seed": "NODE_OPTIONS='--dns-result-order=ipv4first' tsx --env-file .env.local scripts/seed.ts"
    }
  },
